Nexus is digital public infrastructure.

It is built to be freely used, freely shared, and freely learned from —
by individuals, students, educators, and researchers — without cost and
without restriction on that use. It is not built to be a commercial
asset, a product, or a component of anyone's business model.

This license preserves that intent.

