  Use       Run Nexus locally for personal, educational, or research
            purposes, without restriction.

  Share     Copy and redistribute Nexus in any medium or format,
            provided you include this license and attribution to the
            original author.

  Adapt     Modify, build upon, or fork Nexus for non-commercial
            purposes, provided any modified version is released under
            this same license and clearly attributes the original work.

These permissions apply to individuals, students, educators, academic
institutions, nonprofits, and independent researchers. The test is
always the purpose of the use — not the identity of the user.

Use is permitted when it is not primarily intended for or directed
toward commercial advantage or monetary compensation.

